##Three teenagers and a million masks

Wechat, bingdianweekly

Features, China Youth Daily's in depth reporting brand. We believe that news has more than one day of life.

After giving away free face masks.

About 2,197 words

Estimated reading time: 6 minutes

Zhongqingbao Zhongqingwang Wuhan Front Reporting Group

"Today, we received 2,500 disposable surgical masks as medical supplies from our volunteers. I would like to express my sincere thanks to the donors for their immediate emergency assistance. " A young man handed 2,500 masks to workers at the G4201 Wuhan Ring Expressway Toll Booth and received a thank you note.

The Mask Guy is Kang deng-lin, 34. Without stopping, he started the car and disappeared into the night. The next stop, he had to rush back to the warehouse 30 kilometers away, to continue to the next stop distribution of caring masks.

The Masks, 1,053,500 in total, were purchased at his own expense by Jiang Denglin, Zhang Hao and Zhang Fan. From the 23rd, they began to distribute free to Wuhan city hospitals, communities, universities, troops, toll stations, as well as suburban towns and other places. With their help, more than 200 volunteers joined the charity delivery team.

Is there anything you can do

Jiang Denglin is the founder, 2008 to Wuhan University, after graduation in Wuhan to work, 2018 and a friend founded a film and Television Media Company.

On January 21, the 12th of the lunar month, Jiang Deng drove back to his hometown in Loudi, Hunan Province, to spend the Spring Festival with his family. In the face of sudden outbreak, before departure, he went downstairs to the pharmacy to buy masks, general surgical masks have been sold out, he bought three N95 masks, spent 90 yuan, "a bit expensive. ". Home after a search in the e-commerce platform, most of the masks have been sold short.

Wuhan so many citizens, they can not buy masks to do? Jiang Denglin thought "can do something" .

He immediately called Zhang Hao, a good friend who also started his own business in Wuhan, and the two agreed to buy some masks at their own expense and distribute them to Wuhan residents free of charge.

A few minutes later, their mutual friend, Wuhan, a car club President Zhang Fan also joined in, the action team was officially set up, named "Wuhan Spirit. ".

That morning, the trio split up to search for mask suppliers in the province and eventually settled on a factory in Xiantao. When the manufacturer learned that they had bought it at their own expense, they gave it away for free, at a cost, and gave away 40,000 of it.

After lunch on the 22nd, Jiang Deng drove from Loudi and Zhang Hao drove from his hometown in Huanggang to meet in Wuhan to refine the distribution plan.

In Wuhan, Zhang Fan has assembled eight caring vehicles to transport the first 201,000 masks back to Xiantao.

Do a good deed, don't make it worse

In Times of crisis, how can I help with Public Welfare? Zhang Fan is also a veteran rescue team doctor with extensive volunteer and protective experience. At the beginning of the "spirit of Wuhan" campaign, Zhang Fan proposed that all volunteers must protect themselves in accordance with the uniform regulations throughout the whole process; while volunteering, they should disseminate knowledge of scientific protection.

Early on the morning of the 23rd, Zhang Hao contacted the Wuhan Health Department and got the address and telephone number of the Health Department of all administrative districts in the city. At 10 am, the trio and more than a dozen volunteers from the car club began to distribute separately. In the afternoon, 50,000 masks were distributed to several communities where the epidemic was relatively severe.

Volunteers deliver care masks to Wuchang Hospital.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The second batch of masks arrived in Wuhan smoothly on the evening of the 23rd. In order to make it easier for more people to get the masks that night, members of the public can collect two free masks from each of the 35 shops in Wuhan by presenting their ID cards.

The news that "you can get a mask for free with your ID card" spread quickly among wechat groups in Wuhan. More volunteers are joining in to help spread the word and participate in distribution.

The team has also set up an open pick-up point at his office in Hongshan District. That day, nearly 100 calls for help to Jiang Denglin, there are communities, colleges, as well as ordinary citizens. Jiangdeng please them with a good unit proof and personal identity card to come, each person to receive 2 to 10, the unit can receive a little more.

Collection of free face masks.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The love keeps coming together

Can you set up an open collection point in Hankou, too? Liu Xinxin, a volunteer on the team who is a host of Wuhan TV station and an Internet Star of the "Han Ka" talk show, immediately sent the news to his Fan Circle on the afternoon of the 24th.

At 51 Xuesong road in Hankou, Bao Dehong, who runs the restaurant, was the first to step forward. Bao Dehong is Chengdu, originally intended to return home for the Spring Festival, when the epidemic, he persuaded the old home, and his wife and children stay in Wuhan.

Baodehong immediately disinfected the restaurant with his wife and five employees who stayed in Han. Together, they made a table and put up a simple poster with the words "get the mask free" .

At 1800 hours, seven people began to hand out masks. When they see someone on the side of the road without a mask, they stop each other and ask for it. An old man passed by and asked how much the mask cost. The old man thanked him profusely when he heard that it was free.

On the 24th, the news of some hospitals'shortage of face masks gradually converged on the action team. On that day, at 21:40 on the 30th of the Lunar New Year, Zhang Fan was on his way to Union Hospital and Wuhan City Hospital when a reporter from the Central Youth Daily, the youth and Youth Daily, contacted him.

That day, Zhang Fan and his friends ran a total of 31 hospitals across the city, distribution to free masks. Back in Hankou, the third shipment is on its way from Xiantao to Wuhan. Too late to eat, Zhang Fan tried to apply to the community property manager for mask storage location. Without hesitation, the property manager immediately vacated a warehouse.

Early in the morning after the issuance of masks, we all eat "rice. ".

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
At 2308 hours, the third shipment of 425,000 masks was unloaded. Zhang Fan and his companions were then taken separately overnight to Hankou Hospital, Hanyang Hospital, Tongji Hospital and other places. They also sent 1,000 to the Lucky Star nursing home in Wuchang and another maternity centre. After all this, it was 1:12 a.m. , the first day of the Lunar New Year.

And "Wuhan Spirit" Wechat Group, around the last batch of masks how to distribute, as well as protective clothing, disinfectant and other material issues, continue to brush screen until dawn.

That night, the volunteers overnight out of the major hospitals in Wuhan shortage of the latest information table. On the 25th, the first day of the first lunar month, the distribution is continuing, new volunteers are also constantly joining, love is also constantly gathering.

Six students from the Nanjing University of Information Science and Technology donated 516.60 yuan to the action group after learning about their charitable activities through the Internet. The team members unanimously thanked him and wrote a memo.

A netizen nicknamed "turnip" donated 500 yuan. "Don't mention it. We're all doing our best for our family. "

Liu Xinxin has also been busy, shooting and collecting some videos of the event, preparing to make a small documentary and create a talk show to record the Special Spring Festival for his friends.

Early on the morning of the 26th, Jiang Deng and his partners again overnight contact disinfection water and other items, ready to buy gifts to the hospital and the public. Busy until the wee hours of the morning, he said he also had a new life experience, "to do a meaningful thing, everyone will come to help you. "
